      "description": "CFD-predicted pressure rise across 5 flow-speed operating points compared against FDA benchmark experimental measurements. Agreement within 8% at all conditions. Uncertainty in experimental pressure transducer readings characterised via GUM-compliant Type B analysis; CFD numerical uncertainty estimated via Richardson extrapolation on three grid levels.",
      "hasUncertaintyQuantification": "https://uofa.net/synth/uq/uq-pressure-rise-gum"
